title: How to Take Care Of Yourself and Lose Weight
itunes:title: How to Take Care Of Yourself and Lose Weight
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Have you ever thought, "If I go to the gym then I am choosing me over spending time with my child"?

Or, "If I have to work late then I'm choosing my job over my health"?

Losing weight is not a you or me thing. It's a series of choices and today we teach why you have to quit making this an inner battle.
